%% cloud-transfer queued upload/download lifecycle.
flowchart TB
  Producer["On-device producer<br/>(recorder, roi, other service)"] -->|IPC enqueue| Queue["cloud-transfer queue"]
  Queue --> Pick["Pick next job"]
  Pick --> Presign["Request presigned URL<br/>from Cloud API"]
  Presign -->|ok| PutGet["HTTPS PUT / GET<br/>to object store (S3/MinIO)"]
  Presign -->|error / retry| Backoff["Backoff + retry"]
  Backoff --> Pick
  PutGet -->|success| Done["Mark complete<br/>report status via IPC"]
  PutGet -->|fail| Backoff
  Done --> Notify["Publish status →<br/>MQTT …/service/cloud-transfer/status"]
  Notify --> CloudUI["Cloud UI transfers page"]

  classDef dev fill:#EEF9F1,stroke:#2E7D32,color:#123D17;
  classDef cloud fill:#F4EEFF,stroke:#6A42C2,color:#2D1A57;
  class Producer,Queue,Pick,Presign,PutGet,Backoff,Done,Notify dev;
  class CloudUI cloud;
